{"tid":234298,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【以身試伏？】$280全港最貴海南雞飯 秋生絕望︰火都嚟！","createTime":"2017-05-08T07:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T10:56:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c784a002ea80018fc126293e39f9de266b7c49c","tid":234298,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T07:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170507/large/1494155322_af2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170507%2Flarge%2F1494155322_af2e.jpg&h=2031b281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年05月08日<br />\n<br />\n香港君悅酒店的海南雞飯，每份售$280，堪稱是全城最貴，不過一樣出事。話說一向識飲識食的黃秋生，甫知道君悅海南雞飯被譽為全港最好食，就立即去試，怎料翌日就在facebook出post話「真係食到火都嚟」，指完全沒有海南雞飯風味，九唔搭八。記者就此事致電秋生哥問個究竟，他說，「簡直是絕望，不是失望，是絕望！雞無味，飯沒有雞油及香料味。湯更加荒謬，以為有金華火腿，原來是乾葱頭！」他說吃完第一啖飯已經叫侍應來，怎料侍應很緊張，反問要否給他大廚電郵來個直接對話。「如叫君悅雞皇飯，沒問題，但那一定不是海南雞飯。如果純以雞飯來看也不算精彩，你收這樣高價錢，是矮仔又扮高佬。說到是全香港最貴或最美味，應要將這名字拿下來。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，秋生說這麼多，其實只是希望餐廳能有所改進。而坊間亦很多平靚正海南雞飯推介，如中環的海南寶寶$60外賣海南雞飯，是由曾在君悅任職的大民哥及Chef Eddy所炮製，日日吸引大批中環OL排隊買。想當年，大民哥亦有份調配君悅浸雞的白滷水秘方，不過他們的飯價錢較相宜，夠抵食。而大角嘴的文華雞飯（新加坡），老闆曾在新加坡賣雞飯十多年，會先炒香南薑、蒜頭、乾葱及香茅等，加少許湯、雞油及斑蘭葉煲飯，飯粒粒分明又入味。而由80後開的海南雞小店「聚寶食軒」，就選用較貴的麻黃雞，用大量冰將雞急凍，令雞皮中間脂肪變成啫喱狀，不會油淋淋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170508/56663169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170508%2F56663169&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=540cdf01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170508%2F56663169&h=cf5ae689\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170508/56663169</a>"},{"pid":"40c2e371e6243bfba7102e1dfb3be5a8c49050cd","tid":234298,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"280蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa88ec573dc6a3d9ba37a9a89239df810fcc1b52","tid":234298,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"食過自助餐係唔錯wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過直接比$280食又真係唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7beeb149d28f9b995f0904696bb473f829b252e","tid":234298,"uid":33524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"君悅雞皇飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4c1ade609c1901151542a5813b92fb0ca9e410","tid":234298,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"聚寶抵食"},{"pid":"0c6860b89d49ccc251d7705f33c0870d4f6b345c","tid":234298,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"好多年前俾個fd夾我去食過一次<br />\n嗰時好似200定250左右<br />\n唔係難食，但唔覺有咩咁特別<br />\n佢仲一路食一路講到天上有地下無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家仲做梗爛鬼飲食blogger，害人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e5728126ca10fa8198dad170c200d9f3d22ae9","tid":234298,"uid":111971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聚寶抵食</blockquote><br />\n紅磡廣場對面， 正"},{"pid":"7efac2300b4c050dcfd6fcb59a374bd049721993","tid":234298,"uid":29773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"秋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}